{"id":9523,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" align=center><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin\"><FONT size=5>广西是上世纪</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=5 face=Cambria>50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin\"><FONT size=5>年代较早出现饿死人事件的省份</FONT></SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>上世纪</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年代后期至</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>60</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年代初，中国发生了罕见的大饥荒，研究者大多认为大饥荒中的非正常死亡人数有三千万人左右。实际上，在“大跃进”之前，已发生因饥荒饿死人的事件。就目前公开的材料看，广西是较早出现严重饿死人事件的省份，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1956</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年发生的“平乐、荔浦和横县因灾饿死人事件”最先被公开曝光，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1957</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>月</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>18</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>日《人民日报》就有一篇通讯：《去年广西因灾饿死人事件是怎样发生和怎样处理的？》，因此广西饿死人事件是全国人民皆知的事。官方承认“全省可以确定因缺粮饿死的有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>550</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>多人，其中以平乐、荔浦和横县为最多，经查明确属饿死的即有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>300</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>多人”。官方总结饿死人事件的原因，说是：“广西第一个五年计划期间，经济稳定、持续发展，人民生活逐步得到改善。在这种情况下，一些领导满足工作成就，滋长了骄傲自满情绪，官僚主义严重，以致造成</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>－</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1956</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年间因灾饿死人这样令人痛心的事件。”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1957</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>月中共中央和国务院处分了广西党政领导，中共广西省委第一书记陈漫远，广西省委书记郝中士、肖一舟，平乐地委书记杨林、副书记何庶民，平乐专署副专员段书香，平乐县委书记矫志周，荔浦县委书记王文、副书记艾治国、副县长李善本，横县县委书记薜秋水等人受到了留党察看、撤职、记大过等处分。（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《广西通志·中共广西地方组织志》，广西人民出版社</FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3>1994</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3>年版，第三篇第二章第四节“处理因灾饿死人事件”，广西地方志在广西地情网</FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3>www.gxdqw.com</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3>上均可查阅</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>然而，广西最先发生饿死人的现象，不是上述三县最先，在各县志有记载的包括：</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1954</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年阳朔县已经因统购统销导致非正常死亡。阳朔县</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1954</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年粮食总产量</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>4349</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>万公斤，征购粮</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1945</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>万公斤，比</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1953</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年增加</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>16</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>％，占粮食总产量的</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>45</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>％。全县人均口粮只有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>166</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>公斤。这一年发生因缺粮而造成非正常死亡现象。（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《阳朔县志》第二十三章第一节</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>官方承认</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年农民因缺粮而饿死的有：</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>灵川县，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年夏，“因上年粮食随征带购数量过大，部分农村出现粮荒。有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>22436</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人浮肿，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>610</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人非正常死亡（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>含临桂</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）。”（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《灵川县志·总述·大事记》</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>临桂县，“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年因自然灾害和上年部分地区购粮过多，造成一些农民缺粮。全县（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>含灵川</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>13753</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人流入城市行乞，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>22436</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人浮肿，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>610</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人非正常死亡。”（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《临桂县志》第二十二篇第一章第三节</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>合浦县，“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年春，全县有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>5000</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人因饥荒患营养性水肿病，死亡</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>33</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人。”（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《合浦县志》第五篇第五十九章第三节</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>上林县，“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年春夏两季，由于对农户摸底不清、估产过高，再加上统购中工作草率，强制命令，购了农民的过头粮，农村粮食紧张，有些农民因缺粮而患浮肿病，甚至有些人饿死。后来从贵州调来</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>80</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>万斤红米才解除了困难。”（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《上林县志》第二篇第十章第一节</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>由上述官修地方志透露的情况可以看出，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年广西不少县份发生了因统购统销政策执行中估产过高、征购过多而导致饿死人的事件。还有一些地方志没有明确说出饿死人的真相，但从透露的信息来看，是可以推断发生严重饿死人事件的，如浦北县，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年“县内痢疾、水肿病流行，患营养不良性水肿病</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>10639</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人”，“春、夏荒，全县断粮者最多时达</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>226955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人，到</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>月份止，政府发放救济款</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>57948</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>元，救济</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>13390</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>户，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>132350</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>人”。（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《浦北县志·大事记》</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoTitle style=\"MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 3pt\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin\"><STRONG><FONT size=5>广西部分地方志隐瞒或篡改了人口死亡率数据</FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>从公开出版的地方志看，有些地方志隐瞒或篡改了</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年代的人口死亡率数据。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>由于</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1950</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>～</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1961</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年的人口死亡率是敏感资料，所以有的县在修县志时不收录人口死亡率。《环江县志》（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>全名《环江毛南族自治县志》</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）省略了</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1951</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1952</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1953</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1954</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1956</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1958</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1959</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年的人口死亡率。其实环江县的</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年代历年人口死亡数据除了在《全国少数民族人口论文资料选编》有记载之外，在《崛起的壮乡——新中国五十年（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>广西卷·资料篇</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）》（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>中国统计出版社</FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3>1999</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3>年版，以下简称《崛起的壮乡》</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）中也有记载，而这两部书出版时间都早于《环江县志》。《横县县志》不收录任何年份的人口死亡率，《荔浦县志》里没有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1950</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>～</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1956</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年的人口死亡率。其他不收录死亡率的县志包括：富川、博白、上思、阳朔、宾阳、德保、那坡、扶绥、隆安、蒙山、大新、龙胜、武宣等县的县志。不收录</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年代死亡率的有：钟山县、西林县从</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1964</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年起开始有死亡率数据，金秀县从</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1965</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年起有死亡率记载，兴安县只有</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1967</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年后死亡率数据。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>对于官方故意编出的假数据，一般是没有办法查明的，但是一些在曾经合并后又分开的县的数据是可以从另一个县的数据考证出来的。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 黑体\"><FONT size=3>（一）富川县与钟山县的对比<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>富川县与钟山县在</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1953</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年被合并为富钟县，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1962</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>月又恢复原富川县和原钟山县。按这一历史背景，人口死亡率比例应该相同。《钟山县志》记载：</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1956</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年，“由于</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1953</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>～</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年连续三年高征购，农民缺粮情况严重，致使全县发生粮荒。不少农民以野菜、树根充饥，一些乡村出现饿死人现象。”“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1960</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-them","title":"地方志中的五十年代广西饿死人事件","time":1402121785000}